WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Start at the top of the portal. It shows your current stage, what RGS is doing, and your next step.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Look for what needs attention next. The portal keeps the important owner-level signals from scattering.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:23.000
Open one assigned tool at a time. RGS reveals tools based on the stage and lane of the engagement.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:31.000
RGS reviews submitted information before it shapes the next plan or client-facing output.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:38.000
The portal keeps the work organized. RGS helps you see what to repair, and the decisions remain yours.

